{"type":"message","id":"7855aa7a","parentId":"1d2dce87","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:08:43.871Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `temporal_invariance_classifier.ps1` was not saved - the mutation was proposed but the process exited with code 1 before the file could be created. This is a known issue with the pulse script. Let me check if there's a `logs/` directory where the script was supposed to run from.\n\nActually, looking at the log output more carefully:\n\n```\n[mutation proposed] temporal_invariance_classifier.ps1\n```\n\nBut the file wasn't created. This seems like the Python parser/extractor didn't actually create the file.\n\nLet me also check the exit code - it was 1. This could mean the LLM response was truncated or the Python mutation parser failed.\n\n\nI should try generating the TIC classifier myself since the pulse cycle didn't successfully persist it.","thinkingSignature":"61c203ffff11fd1735ae180100c1dcb116ac577b2fa82e8678dd5b23f2d1122a"},{"type":"text","text":"The pulse ran but the mutation failed to persist — the process exited with code 1 before the file could be written. Let me apply the intended mutation now:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lytaqfg3cpet_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1","limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2620,"output":235,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774328917439}}
{"type":"message","id":"df6e5038","parentId":"7855aa7a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:08:43.880Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lytaqfg3cpet_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# pulse.ps1\n# Stateless autonomous pulse for sandbox\n# Each execution: read files -> apply pending mutations -> reason -> propose mutations -> log -> exit\n\nparam(\n    [string]$SandboxRoot = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\",\n    [string]$LLMApiKey = \"\",\n    [string]$LLMModel = \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n    [switch]$AutoAccept = $false   # auto-apply ALL proposed mutations without prompting\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\nSet-Location $SandboxRoot\n\n$timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HHmmss\"\n$logFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_$timestamp.md\"\n\n# Git pull\ngit pull 2>$null | Out-Null\n\n# Read core files\n$goalsFile   = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\current_goals.md\"\n$pendingFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\pending_actions.md\"\n$stanceFile  = \"$SandboxRoot\\identity\\INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md\"\n$stance      = if (Test-Path $stanceFile) { Get-Content $stanceFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\n$goals       = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"No goals file.\" }\n$pending     = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"No pending file.\" }\n\n# Recent pulse\n$recentPulse = Get-ChildItem \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_*.md\" | Sort LastWriteTime -Descending | Select -First 1\n\n[262 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774328923878}}
